Package org.testsuite.app

In this package, all classes will summarized, indicating the test app.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ValidationEventListener
    Defines all events for the validation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    Window that the test app displays.
    AppTreeModel
    Lists the tests on a tree.
    Colors
    Saves the colors for the app
    DlgConfig
    From this class all configuration dialogs are derived.
    DlgConfigGeneral
    Configuration dialog for the general configuration.
    DlgConfigLibrary
    Configuration dialog for the libraries.
    DlgConfigTest
    Configuration dialog for the tests.
    DlgConfigTestRunner
    Configuration dialog for the TestRunner.
    DlgConfigTestSuite
    Configuration dialog for the TestSuite.
    TestRun
    Thread in which the tests are run.
    TestRunnerRenderer
    Displays the tests in tree on.
    ValidationEvent
    Saves all necessary data for the validation event.
    ValidationEventRenderer
    Prepares the Validation errors and outputs them in the list.
